snippet: Since March 2011, nearly 70 Tibetans have self-immolated, and the number on Wednesday was the highest in a single day.
abstract: At least four Tibetans set themselves on fire to protest Chinese rule in Tibetan areas.
lead_paragraph: Since March 2011, nearly 70 Tibetans have self-immolated, and the number on Wednesday was the highest in a single day.

headline.main: China: At Least 4 Tibetans Set Themselves on Fire in Protest
